âœ… Best Practices
Area	Best Practice
âœ… Routing	Use consistent RESTful routes (e.g., /api/products/{id})
âœ… DTOs	Use DTOs always, avoid exposing entities
âœ… Model Validation	Use [Required], [Range] in DTOs, validate with ModelState.IsValid
âœ… Status Codes	Return appropriate responses: 200, 201, 400, 404, 500
âœ… Dependency Injection	Use services/repositories via DI
âœ… Exception Handling	Use global exception middleware
âœ… Logging	Use structured logging with Serilog/NLog
âœ… Security	Use JWT Bearer Token Authentication
âœ… Versioning	Use v1, v2 in routes or headers
âœ… Documentation	Use Swagger (OpenAPI) and customize it
